            <div class="w-full md:w-2/3 bg-white h-full flex p-3.5 md:p-6 rounded-lg">
                <div class="my-4 md:my-0 cursor-pointer hidden md:block">
                    <img src="/assets/icon/pdf.svg" alt="pdf-icon" title="Download Dokumen">
                </div>

                <div class="accordion__wrapper w-full md:w-2/3 h-96 md:h-full max-h-full overflow-y-scroll p-2 grow">
                    {% for i in range(0,10) %}
                        <div class="mb-2 bg-white hover:bg-hijau-keraton hover:text-white cursor-pointer">
                            <div class="accordion w-full px-3.5 py-6 relative border border-black flex">
                                <div class="h-10 w-10 bg-hijau-keraton flex items-center justify-center key-note text-white mr-3.5">w</div>
                                <div class="grow flex justify-between">
                                    <div class="bentuk w-full">
                                        <h1 class="font-bold">Bentuk</h1>
                                        <p>Pencu</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bahan w-full hidden md:block">
                                        <h1 class="font-bold">Bahan</h1>
                                        <p>Perunggu</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="kualitas w-full hidden md:block">
                                        <h1 class="font-bold">Kualitas Bahan</h1>
                                        <p>Bagus</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="panel h-fit min-h-28 p-3.5 pt-0 text-justify hidden">
                                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Illo inventore distinctio autem, ipsum quasi aut eveniet sint. Facere, voluptatum reprehenderit illo maiores officia nam error a corrupti, repudiandae pariatur ea. Lorem
